The paper presents a framework for object discovery, detection, tracking, and reconstruction using RGBD cameras and a robot manipulator. The system performs dense 3D simultaneous localization and mapping concurrently with unsupervised object discovery. The paper involves robotics (cs.RO), computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.AI), and pattern recognition (cs.LG) techniques. The paper also involves control systems (cs.SY) as the robot manipulator is used to gain additional motion-cues. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories are cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, and cs.SY.
